---
title: Prawn Pad Thai with Sweetcorn and Green Beans
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Prawn Pad Thai in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/prawn-pad-thai-7bb184d7-c94831de.jpg
